snippet.title: Amber Heard has world’s most beautiful face - according to scientific theory
snippet.description:
Beauty is in the eye of the beholder, but a recent scientific study of celebrities' facial features suggests that beauty can be more specifically defined. Amber Heard, currently in the middle of a nasty split with husband Johnny Depp, takes the crown as having the most attractive face. 

Amber Heard has world’s most beautiful face, perfect eyebrows, according to science.

Amber had the highest percentage for perfect features and also had the best chin and nose, according to scientific facial mapping software.
